    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Restore the Ecosystems of the Multiverse</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Garden and a Goat invites you to rescue animals and restore ecosystems in this casual, relaxing, single-player animal collecting game. Your robot is placed into a multiverse of gardens where you are needed most. Each garden needs your help to get the local animals to return and join you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/50164c67526e0a4d01d793288aeb743a.poster.avif?t=1771298670\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/50164c67526e0a4d01d793288aeb743a.webm?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/50164c67526e0a4d01d793288aeb743a.mp4?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome the Animals Back with Affection and Treats!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nurture each environment back to life by removing weeds and rubble, planting the local plants, and attracting animals to the revived garden. When animals visit, pet them, feed them treats you make, and place decos they like to encourage them to stay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/ea07893a30470fafc08578158a7e6802.poster.avif?t=1771298670\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/ea07893a30470fafc08578158a7e6802.webm?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/ea07893a30470fafc08578158a7e6802.mp4?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use Handy Tech to Help with the Recovery</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use tech consoles and the cheerful drone as some of your tools along the way. Scan and harvest &quot;data gems&quot;, which are the garden currency used to add more plants, animals, and decorations. With these, you'll also be able to puzzle out secret animal requirements to collect exotic looking, rare multiverse variants!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/d507e8ec0edbeff417842549607235d5.poster.avif?t=1771298670\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/d507e8ec0edbeff417842549607235d5.webm?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/d507e8ec0edbeff417842549607235d5.mp4?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock New Plants, Recipes, Rewards, and More!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along your journey, unlock new crops to plant and harvest, recipes for tasty treats to make at the treat console, and decorations and cosmetic rewards to both beautify your garden and your robot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/cdbb08a83d449cc75f8131afabbc7c83.poster.avif?t=1771298670\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/cdbb08a83d449cc75f8131afabbc7c83.webm?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156550/extras/cdbb08a83d449cc75f8131afabbc7c83.mp4?t=1771298670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh… and there's a multiverse goat keeping you company and bringing mystery, mischief, and presents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
